English.Text: "Something just as rare and no less magical!" chuckles your zoologist, and proceeds to dive after the creature, resurfacing a short while later. "Poor little soul seems to have been separated from its mother," your zoologist splutters, clutching a juvenile specimen of an obscure sea-dweeling species. "Would you chaps kindly running her a bath? I think we better take her with us." From now on, whenever your crew feel sad, they can stop by the creature's tub and enjoy its special warblings.
